---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="Ecosystem and Public Presence | Rank4AI" description="Rank4AI ecosystem – all social profiles, distribution platforms, and community presence across 42+ platforms.">
<section class="pt-12 pb-24">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <p class="section-tag">Ecosystem</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">Ecosystem and Public Presence</h1>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-10">Rank4AI maintains an active presence across 42+ platforms and sources. Every profile uses the same entity description. Every link points back to rank4ai.co.uk. This is how we practice what we preach – building the connected digital footprint that AI systems trust.</p>

    <h2 class="mb-4">Social Profiles</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-3 mb-10">
      <a href="https://x.com/rank4ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card text-center text-sm font-medium">X / Twitter</a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/rank4ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card text-center text-sm font-medium">LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/rank4ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card text-center text-sm font-medium">Instagram</a>
      <a href="https://www.facebook.com/rank4ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card text-center text-sm font-medium">Facebook</a>
      <a href="https://www.tumblr.com/rank4ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card text-center text-sm font-medium">Tumblr</a>
      <a href="https://www.threads.net/@rank4ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card text-center text-sm font-medium">Threads</a>
      <a href="https://pinterest.com/rank4ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card text-center text-sm font-medium">Pinterest</a>
      <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@rank4ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card text-center text-sm font-medium">TikTok</a>
    </div>

    <h2 class="mb-4">Distribution &amp; Authority</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-3 mb-10">
      <a href="https://medium.com/@info_98087" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card text-center text-sm font-medium">Medium</a>
      <a href="https://substack.com/@rank4aiuk" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card text-center text-sm font-medium">Substack</a>
      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@Rank4AI" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card text-center text-sm font-medium">YouTube</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/AdamParkerRank4AI" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card text-center text-sm font-medium">GitHub</a>
      <a href="https://clutch.co/profile/rank4ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card text-center text-sm font-medium">Clutch</a>
      <a href="https://www.goodfirms.co/company/rank4ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card text-center text-sm font-medium">GoodFirms</a>
      <a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/ai-search-explained-by-rank4ai/id1877874966" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card text-center text-sm font-medium">Apple Podcasts</a>
      <a href="https://open.spotify.com/show/4r0S7lAO4aXNb9LfacH86A" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card text-center text-sm font-medium">Spotify</a>
    </div>

    <h2 class="mb-4">Governance &amp; Verification</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3 mb-10">
      <a href="https://find-and-update.company-information.service.gov.uk/company/16584507" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card text-center text-sm font-medium">Companies House</a>
      <span class="card text-center text-sm font-medium">ICO Registered</span>
      <span class="card text-center text-sm font-medium">Google Business Profile</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
